{"id": 1061, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都为自己的爱美/颜控，付出过什么代价？", "description": "苦点累点没什么，美就行啦！（题图来自：Lauren Tamaki）", "record_count": 2372, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183544JDjf64KhMEIcakUv.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-11T03:00:21Z", "options": [{"id": 97114, "content": "自觉找的难看所以很讨厌拍照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 264156}, {"id": 97280, "content": "一周不吃饭，结果就瘦下来了，再也没有达到过那个时期的标准了了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675279}, {"id": 97281, "content": "每天用发蜡，超级烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593531}, {"id": 97282, "content": "天天上张大妈海淘各种潮物。一周买了解双鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676257}, {"id": 100356, "content": "用剃须刀 把眉毛剃了  花了个大口子  现在眉毛连一起了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685061}, {"id": 97548, "content": "不戴眼镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670887}, {"id": 97297, "content": "想整容想疯了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645236}, {"id": 98322, "content": "买了一堆美貌的本子舍不得用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680452}, {"id": 99605, "content": "人丑还颜控，活该单身–––大多数人的真实写照", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683498}, {"id": 97306, "content": "很冲动的买了一双很贵的鞋子，结果没穿出去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676368}, {"id": 97568, "content": "每天提前两小时起床，晚上敷完面膜再睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674753}, {"id": 97317, "content": "花两个月工资请私教健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667742}, {"id": 100648, "content": "隐形眼镜把?磨出血。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688336}, {"id": 97834, "content": "现在的努力学习就是为了去韩国整容", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678593}, {"id": 97327, "content": "爱照镜子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676670}, {"id": 100143, "content": "上网写一个本子的各种美容的建议", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686180}, {"id": 106800, "content": "因为衣服少，搭配不对而不敢出门", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711860}, {"id": 105525, "content": "lob头夏天热炸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672607}, {"id": 226625, "content": "相册男神照片数量不断上升 看一部剧一部电影一部番就多一个男朋友 手机内存堪忧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094668}, {"id": 99654, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110047}, {"id": 97108, "content": "穿好看的裙子，少吃很多好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601500}, {"id": 97110, "content": "看到好看的瓶子就买饮料，尽管我不爱喝~", "image": null, "praise_count": 154, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644875}, {"id": 97111, "content": "为了穿紧身裙子不显小肚子，穿的那一天基本不吃东西\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674958}, {"id": 100951, "content": "买了再也不会穿的衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688955}, {"id": 97112, "content": "上发蜡上砸了，洗个头重来", "image": null, "praise_count": 88, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254552}, {"id": 97113, "content": "为了不破坏内心对自我形象的好感度，从不照镜子", "image": null, "praise_count": 86, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120571}, {"id": 97115, "content": "夏天再热也披头发 显脸小", "image": null, "praise_count": 141, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459807}, {"id": 97116, "content": "打了2枚牙钉，让牙齿内收3毫米。#3毫米的美丽", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674071}, {"id": 104284, "content": "网上沉迷男色 现实厌男症晚期……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702123}, {"id": 97117, "content": "不自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 330, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671331}, {"id": 97118, "content": "为了矫牙，拔掉四颗恒牙。长出智齿显脸大，再拔两颗。ˊ_>ˋ", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674981}, {"id": 97119, "content": "单身", "image": null, "praise_count": 232, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423216}, {"id": 97120, "content": "冷天敷面膜", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539921}, {"id": 97121, "content": "每次想吃东西就想着要省钱买好看的，就不吃了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 303018}, {"id": 97122, "content": "短裙高跟小碎步，心好累", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571608}, {"id": 97123, "content": "穿新鞋就下雨", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611598}, {"id": 97124, "content": "我本来就很帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603240}, {"id": 97125, "content": "男神换了一个又一个。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 393869}, {"id": 97126, "content": "买过很多很好看很有趣但不实用的单品", "image": null, "praise_count": 141, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675002}, {"id": 97127, "content": "\b为了小腹不隆起，那么好吃的东西都他妈不吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615702}, {"id": 97128, "content": "每一天都早起洗头发\n头发没吹好 洗了重来", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666428}, {"id": 97129, "content": "坚持化妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675011}, {"id": 97130, "content": "不洗脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672239}, {"id": 97132, "content": "穿高跟鞋行路，明明脚已经痛得想哭?，还要保持笑容和步姿", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673933}, {"id": 97133, "content": "为了美，早起一小时化妆。为了穿紧身裙，保持收腹一整天", "image": "img/option/option/20160711122237D0KtvsBIo31ZfaQP.jpg", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675034}, {"id": 97134, "content": "为了美，早起一小时化妆。为了穿紧身裙，保持收腹一整天", "image": "img/option/option/20160711122534C2AHKMtQpexmOqEo.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675034}, {"id": 97390, "content": "感觉不好看，一看到了会花半小时间整理自己的脸！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676167}, {"id": 97136, "content": "微整形。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662005}, {"id": 97137, "content": "每天早上坚持洗头", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670931}, {"id": 97138, "content": "三伏天大中午裹着裹着保鲜膜跑楼梯，然而并没有瘦几两?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227456}]}